data.description: Indulge in modern prairie luxury with this brand-new construction, a harmonious blend of contemporary design and meticulous craftsmanship. Discover custom features throughout, from the chef's dream kitchen with custom cabinets, walk-in pantry, and oversized gas range, to two en-suites offering private retreats. Upstairs, two additional bedrooms showcase thoughtful design and abundant natural light. The oversized three-car garage with a spacious storage area if perfect for your storage needs. The covered patio, complements the best features of the home allowing you to extending your living space outdoors. Embrace a lifestyle of comfort and sophistication in this meticulously designed home – your sanctuary in the heart of Burley, Idaho.
